parameters: Thief Nora: It's good that there's a suitable place.

Thief Nora: Being alone like this... it reminds me of when
I ran away from the Emma Thief Guild...

Hunter Jaeger: I'm not a suspicious person. I'm a hunter
who has claimed this area as my territory.
Thief Nora: I-I'm sorry...! I'll leave right away...
Thief Nora: U-Um... What is it?

Hunter Jaeger: You have a good physique, you give off a
natural hunter vibe!
Hunter Jaeger: Can I hold you?

Hunter Jaeger: I'm a simple man! I just want to embrace a
beautiful woman, that's all!

Hunter Jaeger: Of course, I'll show my gratitude. But if
you don't like it, you can refuse.
Thief Nora: Um... Ah... I-I'm sorry!
Hunter Jaeger: Ahaha! You don't need to apologize!

Hunter Jaeger: I often hunt in this area, so if you ever
change your mind, feel free to come!
Thief Nora: Y-You're a strange person...

Thief Nora (She had an amazing physique... but... it's a
bit... wasteful--)

Thief Nora: Ah, what am I thinking! I need to hurry and go
back to everyone!

Thief Nora (It's better to have a lot of money for the
journey...)

Thief Nora (And, and... such a manly and amazing physique...
ugh...)

Hunter Jaeger: Is it okay for me to decide if I can embrace
you?
Thief Nora: Um, um... yes... ah... I-I'm fine.

Hunter Jaeger: Ahaha, don't be so nervous! Since you're
here, you should enjoy yourself to the fullest.
Would you like to skip the adult scene?

Hunter Jaeger: You're amazing, treating me, a hunter, like
prey...

Thief Nora: Ugh... I'm sorry... Lately, I haven't been able
to control myself very well...

Hunter Jaeger: I often hunt here, so if you're willing to
be my prey, come here.

Hunter Jaeger: I almost forgot to request a job on the Wald
bulletin board... Please take it for me.

Thief Nora (It's like my body isn't my own... What happened
to me...?)
Do you want to skip the adult scene?
Hunter Jäger: You've come at a good time!
Hunter Jäger: Now, let's enjoy ourselves together!
